[muffled radio voice]

09:02.933 --> 09:07.547
[door squeaks]
[clatters]

09:09.810 --> 09:12.813
-And the great
dragon was cast out,

09:12.943 --> 09:15.467
metal vermin, called the Devil.

09:18.819 --> 09:22.170
And Satan was deceiving
the whole world.

09:23.998 --> 09:25.956
He was cast out!

09:26.087 --> 09:27.741
Do you hear what I--
[voice drowned out]

09:27.871 --> 09:31.266
[items rattling]
[scissors snip]

09:31.396 --> 09:34.095
