The Devil roams among us.

09:34.225 --> 09:35.618
This is where the Devil roams--

09:35.749 --> 09:36.880
[scissors snip]

09:37.011 --> 09:39.970
[squeaking metal]

09:41.450 --> 09:43.974
[door creaks]

09:44.105 --> 09:46.890
[metal squeaks]
